<td align="center"><b>
<i>Hoplitis simplex</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Cresson, 1864&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Heriades simplex </i>Cresson, 1864; <i>Robertsonella simplex </i>&#40;Cresson, 1864&#41;; <i>Robertsonella gleasoni </i>Titus, 1904; <i>Robertsonella crataegina </i>Cockerell, 1909; <i>Robertsonella simplex crataegina </i>Cockerell, 1909; <i>Hoplitis &#40;Robertsonella&#41; gleasoni </i>&#40;Titus, 1904&#41;</small><p>
